<!-- Contains the stats of all creatures.
	Each stat defines how capable the creature is within that category.
		* Strength: The creature's capability to apply force
		* Attack: How much damage the creature can inflict with an attack
		* Armor: How difficult it is to harm the creature
		* Vitality: Amount of damage the creature can withstand
		* Speed: How quickly the creature can travel
		* Dexterity: How quickly the creature can attack
		* Intelligence: Creature's capability to learn and use knowledge
	In addition to the stat categories, there are also traits.
	There are 3 traits in total:
		- Perception: How well the creature can sense things
			* Sight
				+ Blind
				+ Reduced
				+ Normal
				+ Enhanced
			* Hearing
				+ Deaf
				+ Reduced
				+ Normal
				+ Enhanced
			* Smell (or taste)
				+ Anosmic
				+ Reduced
				+ Normal
				+ Enhanced
		- Special: Any unique abilities the creature has (will be elaborated in different file)
		- Appearance might be added later
-->

